'''lemniscate''' 
# The [[symbol]] for [[infinity]], which resembles the figure 8 on its side. 
#{{mathematics}} Any closed [[curve]] (similar to a figure eight) described by a [[Cartesian]] [[equation]] of the form <math>(x^2 + y^2)^2 = a^2 (x^2 - y^2)\,</math>
